'''Mmušôgaê wa Raymond Mhlaba''' ke mmusogae go feta [[Mmasepala Setereke tša Amathole]] wa porofense [[Kapa Bohlabela]] ka moka [[Afrika Borwa]].

Formed after the merger of [[Nkonkobe Mmusogae]] and [[Nxuba Mmusogae]]. [[Toropokgolo]] wa Raymond Mhlaba ke [[Fort Beaufort]].

